<div class="text-center container py-5">
  <p class="cover-heading">You can save <span class="lives">lives</span>. </p>
  <p class="cover-lead">
    Help tackle the coronavirus pandemic.
  </p>
  <a role="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg px-4 mt-3 mb-5 shadow" href="#apply">
    Volunteer
  </a>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_baby_ja7a.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Aid Crews
      </span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-primary align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-walking"></i>
        mobile
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Doctors and nurses donâ€™t only care for their patients, but also their children, parents, and pets. Take care of healthcare workers by volunteering to check in on their loved ones. We need them, and they need you.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_collab_8oes_modified.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Elderly Crews
      </span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-primary align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-walking"></i>
        mobile
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Think of a very transmissive virus just like SARS-CoV-2 but much more deadly. This is what your elderly neighbours deal with. They need your help to survive this pandemic. Assist them with simple tasks like shopping. Do not expose them to even a minor risk by disinfecting every item you hand to them.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_conference_call_b0w6.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">Coordination Crews</span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-success align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
        remote
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Join our team and help us coordinate Pandemic Volunteers. Even a few hours a week can help us achieve our mission. Bring your expertise, or help us coordinate your local teams. However you think you can help, we can use it.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_medical_research_qg4d.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">
        Research Ambassadors
      </span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-success align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
        remote
      </span>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-secondary align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
        requires credentials
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      There are around 140 studies published about COVID-19 every day. Reviewing these studies are crucial in determining the best treatments. However, the medical doctors in the field are not even able to sleep at their homes. Reach out to your local hospital and create a chat group with your doctors. Inform them about latest actionable guidelines. Answer their COVID-19 related questions.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_doctor_kw5l.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">Triage Crews</span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-success align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
        remote
      </span>
      <small class="mx-2 font-weight-bold align-middle" style="font-size: 10pt" >or</small>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-primary align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-walking"></i>
        mobile
      </span>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-danger align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i>
        requires immunity
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Most COVID-19 patients are being sent to home isolation. They don't know how to assess their conditions. Have video calls and help them evaluating their severity. If you are immune, equip yourself with a thermometer and an oximeter to visit critical patients at their homes. Report your neighbours' conditions to your health system through Pandemic Volunteers.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row my-5 mx-0">
  <div class="col-md-4 d-flex text-center justify-content-center">
    <%= inline_svg_tag "graphics/home/undraw_doctors_hwty.svg", size: '200', class: 'm-auto' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <p class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
      <span class="mr-2 align-middle">Hospital Crews</span>
      </br>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-info align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-h-square"></i>
        at hospitals
      </span>
      <span style="font-size: 10pt" class="badge badge-danger align-middle">
        <i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i>
        requires immunity
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      Nurses and other hospital staff work 24/7 at this moment. This unsustainable work demand decreases the quality of medical care and costs lives. Join a group of volunteers at your local hospital to help medical staff. Ease the lives of the heroes of our time. Disinfect personal protective equipment. Help with logistics. Do whatever your local hospital needs you to do.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="offset-md-2 col-md-8 px-0 py-5">
  <div id="apply" class="card shadow">
    <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between pb-0">
      <div class="cover-lead font-weight-bold">
        <p>Apply for volunteering</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body bg-light">
      <!-- /#apply is used to retain form errors and scroll to the form in case of errors -->
      <%= render partial: 'volunteers/form',
                 locals: {
                   volunteer: @volunteer,
                   countries: @countries_collection,
                   states: @states_collection,
                   cities: @cities_collection,
                   volunteer_crews: @volunteer_crews
                 }
      %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= javascript_pack_tag 'location_selector', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "theme" %>
